{"tid":2283569,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【港講藝術】深夜時分，再談「漏單」畫家竇加的幾張畫作","createTime":"2020-11-12T16:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T16:49:20.000Z","uid":17335,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d1f87f69f7431bb49e1fbb55b6f8d6d38eaf015d","tid":2283569,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T16:20:44.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\">「漏單」之外，竇加是何許人？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2KQSnnx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2KQSnnx.jpg&h=27fa535f&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n竇加，法國印象派男團創始成員之一。人人都印象派，唔通人人都想印象派咩？有趣是，竇加否認自己是其中印象派一份子，甚至反感得反對印象派的一切理論。<br />\n<br />\n這位叛逆畫家善於觀察、描繪社會眾生相，雖然他常畫賽馬、劇院等上流活動場景，雙眸卻捕捉繁華背後低下階層的困苦。演員、工人、舞者、乞丐、醉酒、妓女，主流中的小人物 ，全是他繪畫的對象。<br />\n<br />\n這些對象中，芭蕾舞者尤受竇加重視，其時芭蕾伶娜地位不高，有如賣身「藝妓」，大都來自窮苦家庭，戲稱「小老鼠」。這個形容意指少女在台上奔跑跳躍就像老鼠，帶有貶義，諷刺她們卑微的社會身分。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4dHEMPn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4dHEMPn.jpg&h=6489c4f3&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n相反，竇加呈現芭蕾舞者的華麗、活力，他把每一個動作都描繪得栩栩如生。觀者幾乎能感受到舞者下一瞬間的動作，彷彿，隨時都會繼續旋轉不休。<br />\n<br />\n除了讚嘆芭蕾舞的美妙，竇加還透過芭蕾舞者反映社會陰暗面，喜歡躱在樂隊背後，或舞台的角落中作畫，這種特別的構圖角度，潛伏了一絲絲不自在。<br />\n<br />\n在一片芭蕾舞者的曼妙身影之間，黑影和黑衣人不斷鬼魅般顯隱，與純白少女截然不同的西裝男士。不止明顯的舞團樂手、導師，更多影子坐在練習室或後台一角。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AEchyuB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAEchyuB.jpg&h=47a1a43a&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n這些達官貴人坐在練習室或後台，默默注視者舞女們的一舉一動，歇息、聊天、壓腿、拉襪子、跳舞。竇加觀察這些少女身姿，從中物色情婦，那種明星潛規則，反映人性慾望始終如一。<br />\n<br />\n竇加出名孤僻、冷漠和尖酸刻薄，終生未娶，在晚年時身患眼疾，最終失去視力，朋友逐一離他而去。留下的，是他筆下對眾生的如實記錄。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRCEMPM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRCEMPM.jpg&h=0064ae26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</p>"},{"pid":"5a300f5c727f2b61c88c0247eff78e0818bfb056","tid":2283569,"uid":17335,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T16:21:45.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Tuot3v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Tuot3v.jpg&h=af72d2b3&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n想睇更多文藝嘢，歡迎Follow德尼思化：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIG <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/delis.ver/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdelis.ver%2F&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BypFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=272052a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/delis.ver/</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Delisver.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDelisver.hk%2F&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BypFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=00438281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Delisver.hk/</a><br />\nMedium <a href=\"http://bit.ly/36HvepQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36HvepQ&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BypFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=19580605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/36HvepQ</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4cb117c3b3b0dcffad91d5f6a9844cc150d0cd","tid":2283569,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T16:37:20.000Z","msg":"多謝分享！follow先"},{"pid":"ad268f75698d97ea228021878fd8f19287fae801","tid":2283569,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T16:40:43.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a79ed2fd720e02366ea832f35381116270acb88","tid":2283569,"uid":17335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"